@startuml 智慧考试系统UML用例图
' 样式美化（可选）
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #E8F4FD
    BorderColor #2E86AB
    FontName "微软雅黑"
}
skinparam usecase {
    BackgroundColor #F0F8FF
    BorderColor #1E90FF
    FontName "微软雅黑"
}
skinparam arrow {
    Thickness 1.2
    FontName "微软雅黑"
}

' 1. 定义「参与者」（UML标准：actor）
actor 学生 as Student
actor 教师 as Teacher
actor 系统管理员 as Admin
actor 智慧考试系统 as System

' 2. 定义「用例」（UML标准：usecase）
usecase "登录系统" as UC1
usecase "查看考试列表" as UC2
usecase "参加在线考试" as UC3
usecase "查看个人成绩" as UC4
usecase "查看成绩详情" as UC5
usecase "题库管理" as UC7
usecase "手动组卷" as UC8
usecase "发布考试" as UC9
usecase "监控考试过程" as UC10
usecase "成绩统计分析" as UC11
usecase "导出成绩数据" as UC12
usecase "用户管理" as UC14
usecase "角色权限管理" as UC15
usecase "系统监控" as UC16
usecase "数据备份恢复" as UC17
usecase "用户认证" as UC18
usecase "防切屏监控" as UC19
usecase "自动批改" as UC20
usecase "数据统计" as UC21

' 3. 「参与者 ↔ 用例」的关联（直接连线表示“可执行用例”）
Student -- UC1
Student -- UC2
Student -- UC3
Student -- UC4
Student -- UC5

Teacher -- UC1
Teacher -- UC7
Teacher -- UC8
Teacher -- UC9
Teacher -- UC10
Teacher -- UC11
Teacher -- UC12

Admin -- UC1
Admin -- UC14
Admin -- UC15
Admin -- UC16
Admin -- UC17

System -- UC18
System -- UC19
System -- UC20
System -- UC21

' 4. 「包含关系」（<<include>>，被包含的用例是“必须执行”的）
UC3 -[dashed]-> UC1 : <<include>>
UC3 -[dashed]-> UC19 : <<include>>
UC7 -[dashed]-> UC1 : <<include>>
UC8 -[dashed]-> UC7 : <<include>>
UC9 -[dashed]-> UC8 : <<include>>
UC10 -[dashed]-> UC9 : <<include>>
UC11 -[dashed]-> UC20 : <<include>>
UC11 -[dashed]-> UC21 : <<include>>

' 5. 「扩展关系」（<<extend>>，扩展的用例是“可选执行”的）
UC4 -[dashed]-> UC3 : <<extend>>
UC10 -[dashed]-> UC9 : <<extend>>
UC12 -[dashed]-> UC11 : <<extend>>

' 6. 「依赖关系」（<<depend>>，用例“依赖”系统提供的服务）
UC1 -[dashed]-> UC18 : <<depend>>
UC3 -[dashed]-> UC19 : <<depend>>
UC3 -[dashed]-> UC20 : <<depend>>
UC11 -[dashed]-> UC21 : <<depend>>

@enduml
